description.en:
Metti Inu is a 100% decentralized community experiment art meme token on Fantom to spread the love of Pumpametti art. 

50% the Metti Inu supply has been sent to 0xdead and the other half were locked to a Uniswap pool and the LP keys burned. Total supply of Metti Inu is 1 Quadrillion (1,000,000,000,000,000)

So Metti, Much Exquisite!
